            "body": "Hi! I tested #38558 but it didn't fully work for me, it fails on the first `select_parent` call but works after that. The following change works consistently, at least in my current setup:\n\n```lua\nvim.cmd.normal({ 'v'.. vim.keycode('<Esc>'), bang = true })\n-- or\nvim.cmd.normal({ 'v\\27', bang = true })\n```",
